title: Battles - 4 Albums
description:
4 pieces of work from this wonderfully out there band featuring Tyondi Braxton, son of legendary avant-garde jazz composer Anthony Braxton.  Quirky yet friendly explorations that sweep genres from progressive rock, avant pop and just plain unique keep me coming back for more.  

Here are the albums:

Battles
EP C_B EP (considered the best by many fans)
Mirrored (the most recent)
Tonto+

Enjoy and please seed!

Junco
